    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You can change the display format using any python formatter:\n\n```\nIn [21]: pd.options.display.float_format = '{:.4g}'.format\n\nIn [22]: print(DataFrame(dat))\n   column_one  col_two\n0           1   0.0001\n1          10    1e-05\n2         100    1e-06\n3        1000    1e-07\n```\n\nsee python docs http://docs.python.org/2/library/string.html#format-specification-mini-language.\n"
