    "body": "Ok, [I see here](http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/basics.html#console-output-formatting) that `display.float_format` has a default `None`. But what does `None` mean? The actual default is unclear, but using a 'g'-style formatter would be a desirable default.\n"
