    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "As a quick followup, as of version 0.21 (but probably earlier), the default formatting from Pandas is acceptable:\r\n```\r\n   column_one       col_two\r\n0           1  1.000000e-04\r\n1          10  1.000000e-05\r\n2         100  1.000000e-06\r\n3        1000  1.000000e-07\r\n```\r\nnice to see this one addressed over the years!"
